txt.en: Feared by Orcs and dwarves alike, Ushgoth the Mighty leads the forces of Gundabad who dwell in Bekâr-zarakh.
Defeat Ushgoth the Mighty in Bekâr-zarakh
'Well done, [placeholder]! Ushgoth's defeat shall prove a momentous victory in the days to come! Let us return and report your success to Hórin!'
Your mission is to defeat Ushgoth the Mighty, the captain of the Orcs in Bekâr-zarakh.
